   {
      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Thanks for this opening this issue @behradkhodayar. I'd be interested in hearing more of your thoughts on the gRPC features that would be useful for bitcoind (other than streaming). The downsides are explored here but what are all the upsides? Dropping RPC entirely is not realistic but supporting gRPC at some point in the future could be possible (noting Sjors' concerns)",
